rComments: Tough class, but till be amazing at writing by the end. Deadlines are very negotiable and he'll help you as much as you ask.

He's not a professor (he's part of the GEO), but the class is really fun and well constructed. He's a very considerate guys and he's willing to drop things from his curriculum if people don't think it'll work out. Awesome class. Favorite I've taken.
